    <td valign="top" align="left">
    <font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
    <b>Description:</b> <br>
    Direct Damage:  Around 78 Hits of dammage at Level 12.  Range is a little less than bolt spells. Takes a little longer to cast than the lvl 8 shock of ice spell (which, by the way, has a mana cost of 30 and does approx. 34 dmg at lvl 8).<BR>
<BR>
<B>Research:</B><BR>None<br>
    <b>Effects:</b><br>
    Direct Damage
    </font>
    
    </td>
