			This spell can also be found in the Academy of Arcane Science in Freeport.  (In fact, you might as well plan on making a trip to there when you hit<BR>
level 12.  They have the most comprehensive collection of magic vendors I have seen in one place in the entirety of Norrath.  Go to the top floor.)<BR>
<BR>
Frankly, this spell is a godsend for any wizards who have been itching to deal out really spectacular amounts of damage with a single cast, and is the first spell that you will get which can<BR>
do more points of damage against a single opponent than it takes<BR>
to cast.
